<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <title>Order Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #2c3e50;
    }
    .order-box {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 10px;
      border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .order-details {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 10px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .order-details p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: #888;
      font-size: 12px;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Order Confirmation</h1>


    <p>Thank you for your purchase! We are excited to confirm your order for the course <strong><%= order.name %></strong>.</p>

    <div class="order-box">
      <h2>Order Details</h2>
      <div class="order-details">
        <p><strong>Order ID:</strong> <%= order._id %></p>
        <p><strong>Course Name:</strong> <%= order.name %></p>
        <p><strong>Price:</strong> $<%= order.price %></p>
        <p><strong>Date of Purchase:</strong> <%= order.date %></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to reply to this email.</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
